Agnes Ayres https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agnes_Ayres 0 Agnes Ayres (born Agnes Eyre Henkel, April 4, 1898 – December 25, 1940) was an American actress who rose to fame during the silent film era. She was known for her role as Lady Diana Mayo in The Sheik opposite Rudolph Valentino.
